and haven't given it much thought since.<br><br>Do whatever feels the best. You are hopefully here to enjoy yourself. <p>"She just doesn't get that if it doesn't plug in, I'm just not interested." -  <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2735>Xirys</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ullimethemonk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llime the monk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 376<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(8/16/02 8:53:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1769.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Need some advice on starting over</span><hr size=1> I am about to change to Ikky I believe because I screwed up all of my stats and skills. My h2h is about 60 at lvl 47 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><table width="350" border="0"><tr><td width="144"><div align="center"><img src="http://www.geraldfield.com/nadinesplace/calvinquiz/hobbes.gif" width="142" height="125" align="absmiddle"></div></td><td><div align="center"><b><font size="3">You are Hobbes!</font></b><br><font size="2">You're a bit too mellow to be an incarnation of Calvin, but you're still his best pal. You don't mind having fun, though, and enjoy playing tricks on your friends when they least expect it.<br><font size="1">Take the <a href="http://www.geraldfield.com/cgi-bin/unofficial/quizzes/sfesurvey.cgi?whatcalvinareyou" target="_blank">What Calvin are You? Quiz</a> by <a href="mailto:contessina_2000@yahoo.com">contessina_2000@yahoo.com</a>!</font></font></div></td></tr></table><BR><A HREF=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=256092>My Pimpin' Threads</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowr